1. *Cena* je preskupa za to mesto. (The price is too expensive for this place.)
2. On je platio *cenu* za svoju grešku. (He paid the price for his mistake.)
3. Ona i njen suprug su platili *cenu* za njihovu sreću. (She and her husband paid the price for their happiness.)
4. Neki ljudi su spremni da plate *cenu* za uspeh. (Some people are willing to pay the price for success.)
5. *Cene* robe su skočile nakon katastrofe. (The prices of goods rose after the catastrophe.)
6. *Cena* za ulaznice je veoma niska. (The price for tickets is very low.)